      <title>碧桂园寻求再次延期部分境内债券</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-16/country-garden-seeks-to-extend-some-onshore-bonds-again</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，尽管去年进行了一轮延期，但碧桂园控股公司仍将部分境内债券的支付推迟，这突显了这家中国房地产开发商面临的财务压力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-16/country-garden-seeks-to-extend-some-onshore-bonds-again</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 16 Apr 2024 10:04:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>泰晤士水务将于本周发布更新的业务计划</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-16/thames-water-to-release-updated-business-plan-this-week</link>
      <description><![CDATA[泰晤士水务公司董事会成员将于本周进行最后一次谈判，以更新其业务计划，此前股东称其前一份计划“不可投资”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-16/thames-water-to-release-updated-business-plan-this-week</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 16 Apr 2024 10:02:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>尽管受到黑客攻击，联合健康集团的利润仍超出预期</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-16/unitedhealth-beats-profit-estimates-despite-hack-impact</link>
      <description><![CDATA[联合健康集团 (UnitedHealth Group Inc.) 公布的第一季度利润超出了华尔街的预期，并确认了今年的前景，尽管其子公司遭受的网络攻击给医疗保健行业带来了巨大损失。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-16/unitedhealth-beats-profit-estimates-despite-hack-impact</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 16 Apr 2024 10:01:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
